2113.c.Problem Statement:
At $t=0$ a stationary plasma contains a magnetic field

$$
\begin{aligned}
\mathbf{B} &=B(x) \mathbf{e}_{z}, \\
B(x) &= \begin{cases}B_{0}, & |x|<L \\
0, & |x|>L,\end{cases}
\end{aligned}
$$

where $B_{0}$ is a constant. Determine the time evolution of the field assuming that the plasma remains stationary.
